{"tid":891212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"物理治療師要靠父母上車　嘆供樓不快樂：買完後就食屎！","createTime":"2018-11-06T01:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T13:23:45.000Z","uid":34243,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f909ab91c4f986228c7bc4763d48712ef02978","tid":891212,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"香港擁有一大片石屎森林，但港人要在廣袤之間尋方寸立身之所，難度堪比登天。房屋置業階梯已朽，幾百萬人在「樓海」中艱苦尋覓安身之所，劏房戶等公屋、租戶等買樓、業主等供完樓，「樓奴」都在等一個改變命運的機會。<br />\n<br />\n靠父母幹上車，是否真的等於「人生勝利組」？ 物理治療師RT未夠30歲已成為業主，擁有價值千萬的單位，但他卻無半點喜悅。他表示，供樓、家用已佔去每月收入約九成，甚至令他要「犧牲」興趣。供樓負擔重，自己亦不是「金龜」，「我係買完樓之後就食屎！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2054163/org/cb6b8d3a2969996c9a117d7e6a0d67a0.jpg/zxpUhZbohSU3gKaKVyYpCNH9WjLBraeo8lkTZ_JZE2c?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2054163%2Forg%2Fcb6b8d3a2969996c9a117d7e6a0d67a0.jpg%2FzxpUhZbohSU3gKaKVyYpCNH9WjLBraeo8lkTZ_JZE2c%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d0a133c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在荃灣海濱，一排又一排的新樓聳立，其中一個向海單位，正是RT的新居。28歲已經成為業主，RT是社會大眾口中的「人生勝利組」。這個三房海景單位由他一人獨住，樓價約960萬元，晉身有樓一族，對RT而言，喜悅不多：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;我又未去到人哋口中嘅金龜，買完樓後好鬆動，我唔係，我係買完後就食屎！&quot;<br />\nRT</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051627/org/158aba0a256a801afff8c4ee2ad29471.jpg/xaP39M157xI1yh9qdyp9uqQVd0PO4Kv7ErP1NxKz9Tc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051627%2Forg%2F158aba0a256a801afff8c4ee2ad29471.jpg%2FxaP39M157xI1yh9qdyp9uqQVd0PO4Kv7ErP1NxKz9Tc&h=36f66587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨享三房海景單位的RT，直言置業對他而言並非樂事。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\nRT：退休前只剩下3年時間儲錢<br />\n<br />\n去年RT靠父母的退休金，成功買下一個荃灣西新盤「上車」。RT說，當初父母本著「買磚頭最穩陣」的道理，令他「半逼半自願」地踏上業主路。成為業主後，不少人前來恭賀，但他卻說：「壓力來源，係你知道自己將來要供款30年，我唔知自己會唔會有咩冬瓜豆腐&hellip;&hellip;我要保持現時（財政）狀態到57歲，我先會甩難，但我到時候只係啱啱供完樓，退休前只剩下3年時間儲錢，到時都唔知儲到啲咩。」<br />\n<br />\nRT說，自己月入大約4萬元，但供樓連家用，未計三餐交通，已佔收入約九成，每月只剩下3000多元可用。他笑言，幸好自己生活從不奢華，影響才不算不大。不過，他收樓時首次見到「實物」，不諱言單位比想像中細，「真係又貴又細」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051691/org/be96e3318fc83797c85c70c15a81864a.jpg/5mwijPqoLdJebOJya4Z6PDGKK1FHVmAB3Jwo39ycKN8?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051691%2Forg%2Fbe96e3318fc83797c85c70c15a81864a.jpg%2F5mwijPqoLdJebOJya4Z6PDGKK1FHVmAB3Jwo39ycKN8%3Fv%3Dw640&h=814b162b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051693/org/110a230340b003a0cdb006f34efcf6c0.jpg/j0e--UL3LmQ0Hevyroo-WiumsyWfGkKLRpgcCUaYHAk?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051693%2Forg%2F110a230340b003a0cdb006f34efcf6c0.jpg%2Fj0e--UL3LmQ0Hevyroo-WiumsyWfGkKLRpgcCUaYHAk%3Fv%3Dw640&h=375c403b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051694/org/31cca100a36e53f1794f97ed984a682d.jpg/BEq0-64LZ_Jph68sXYMmWj2rSbH8xCXDl1RnMZdUZzE?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051694%2Forg%2F31cca100a36e53f1794f97ed984a682d.jpg%2FBEq0-64LZ_Jph68sXYMmWj2rSbH8xCXDl1RnMZdUZzE%3Fv%3Dw640&h=96b0a1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051706/org/984cb8bc54e8eed7d7930f4cd327e872.jpg/BtKHf86wm-UgTgKEPzw5NFmh4RX1UAezAUljQwFJY0M?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051706%2Forg%2F984cb8bc54e8eed7d7930f4cd327e872.jpg%2FBtKHf86wm-UgTgKEPzw5NFmh4RX1UAezAUljQwFJY0M%3Fv%3Dw640&h=f0549162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2054164/org/e50a63fe3a44b4c93f61520615160f73.jpg/PlFb04V8R-xUP9UhPjl1WffV9SRKmLYGfSn4rH0p-Kw?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2054164%2Forg%2Fe50a63fe3a44b4c93f61520615160f73.jpg%2FPlFb04V8R-xUP9UhPjl1WffV9SRKmLYGfSn4rH0p-Kw%3Fv%3Dw640&h=f951017b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"410605d659c69d00e8905b2dfcd9d3010870ef6b","tid":891212,"uid":34243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:59:58.000Z","msg":"生活與結他只能二擇一<br />\n<br />\n不少香港人窮一生只為一層樓，但RT卻志不在此：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;人生只得一次，you only live once，你將人生目標擺係幢樓到，好物質化&hellip;&hellip;物質上比到我嘅開心，唔係心靈上嘅滿足。&quot;<br />\nRT</span></span><br />\n<br />\nRT一直醉心音樂及運動，閒時會與朋友「夾Band」，對樂器有一定要求，有隊友更曾買入一枝逾萬元結他，並為它戲謔改名為「首期」。見到心儀樂器，RT的確會心動，但做了業主後只能「忍手」，因為他選擇了「真首期」，將興趣的花費都改放在磚頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051711/org/9d81259b016d84c90cf01f3ee70e0207.jpg/Sgw_-IYfL0MtEGwDFvTJCCugvCvbM6pUIky6pCJMuqQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051711%2Forg%2F9d81259b016d84c90cf01f3ee70e0207.jpg%2FSgw_-IYfL0MtEGwDFvTJCCugvCvbM6pUIky6pCJMuqQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a17e310f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRT自供樓後，已難以負擔貴價結他。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n買樓似街市　慢一秒無得揀<br />\n<br />\n樓市瘋狂，相信香港人不會反對。RT回想買樓當日情景，仍心有餘悸，「原本想買兩房單位，但揀樓嗰陣話售罄。」<br />\n<br />\n他形容當時感覺「震撼」，人人爭先恐後。「好似去咗街市咁，遲一秒決定就隨時無得揀。」他最後考慮工資增長及負擔能力，決定轉為買入三房單位，較預算的800萬多出近200萬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&quot;當時我好猶豫，壓力好大，我記得我媽媽喺我後邊，佢扯住我衫尾話唔好&hellip;&hellip;到你點頭話要，一下子就無咗960萬，好似好草率，但你見到大家都好熾熱期待，好似唔使錢咁。&quot;<br />\nRT</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051727/org/5ccb70d7922afe204fbfbae82bcf6877.jpg/VwDBaELjbg4Lvw4sPKXsH8E0o7EDTVPl9TQehfU0HoU?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051727%2Forg%2F5ccb70d7922afe204fbfbae82bcf6877.jpg%2FVwDBaELjbg4Lvw4sPKXsH8E0o7EDTVPl9TQehfU0HoU%3Fv%3Dw640&h=8a52f3e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2051728/org/b70b2e37fcfe10e5c9e78487f3292678.jpg/B2hRBBe7svnhh4ydezavIxg3eHSMR931BPzfAQT83wE?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2051728%2Forg%2Fb70b2e37fcfe10e5c9e78487f3292678.jpg%2FB2hRBBe7svnhh4ydezavIxg3eHSMR931BPzfAQT83wE%3Fv%3Dw640&h=550cdd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個人供樓：「我都知好離地」<br />\n<br />\n對置業不以為然的他，最後卻要參與其中。他慨嘆在香港若不及早置業，只能眼看樓價一直升，「遲早都要住，我呢一刻唔諗，過多5年一樣要諗，除非我唔結婚唔生仔，如果我呢一刻唔打算，咁到時點算？」 <br />\n<br />\n在現時的樓市，年輕人可以買樓、自己一個人供樓，RT都說覺得聽起來「離地」。他又說，自己任職物理治療師月入約4萬元，若沒有父母幫忙，肯定難以負擔樓價，「我呢一類人，已經叫做專業人士&hellip;&hellip;香港入息中位數係1.8萬元，我係佢哋兩倍有多，但我自己一個都儲唔到首期，咁其他人點算？」"},{"pid":"941d4bdfb4a4d5fe4c3c4c927180898c560929d4","tid":891212,"uid":106278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"上車買新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c34b3729adc54995e4ff83d22d4d16fa0faf141","tid":891212,"uid":34243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"RT好靚仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e8ab0b5cb69d729f0d359f0c480dbd6622411e","tid":891212,"uid":174940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"嘩咁慘慘豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e531a00c1efdfda10e8ac07c6300f0b8957516","tid":891212,"uid":154725,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"「我呢一類人，已經叫做專業人士&hellip;&hellip;香港入息中位數係1.8萬元，我係佢哋兩倍有多，但我自己一個都儲唔到首期，咁其他人點算？」<br />\n<br />\n真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4ab962c6e984a356cd506d2849b6f4147c3149","tid":891212,"uid":147367,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"邊個叫你一黎就買成千萬既樓<img src=\