T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"你咪理，上到會先"},{"pid":"0b4c4934d2993f7f77a626052de2d34e44d41331","tid":891212,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"267b9c7e3afa6f94c7aeecae607a123b0bed6f8b","tid":891212,"uid":46407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"645 實 賣960 講到咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左SSD 當打個和賣返出去喇屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"而家俾SSD, 應該開開心心打過和"},{"pid":"4e7f4ba35ad24d6dbce86bf856b7767184631c6d","tid":891212,"uid":59746,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"一條友買3房海景新樓<br />\n之後怨供唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3df5340cdc31f8bc4acff1268317b04b09274d","tid":891212,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7716e875516e3d2eed43bf1863007ec900ffc568","tid":891212,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"又有物理治療牌又有樓仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616c562942ff272307fa134657453005a6a4d823","tid":891212,"uid":147367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"RT說，當初父母本著「買磚頭最穩陣」的道理，令他「半逼半自願」地踏上業主路。<br />\n<br />\n當時我好猶豫，壓力好大，我記得我媽媽喺我後邊，佢扯住我衫尾話唔好&hellip;&hellip;到你點頭話要，一下子就無咗960萬，好似好草率，但你見到大家都好熾熱期待，好似唔使錢咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母叫你唔好買咁貴，你自己死都要買"},{"pid":"b2e578a778d36370f3f06418bb895db11d919bcd","tid":891212,"uid":54452,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"點解咁得閒接受訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown